data.description: Discover the charm of this 3-bed, 2-bath home nestled on a large corner lot! Come inside to find an inviting living room that perfectly flows onto the kitchen. Vaulted ceilings add to the airy feel, complemented by a skylight. The dining/family room is a versatile space with sliding doors that create a seamless indoor-outdoor flow. The kitchen boasts an SS Elec range and ample cabinetry w/pull-out drawers. Main bedroom has a full bathroom for added comfort. Laundry room comes with built-in shelving & cabinets. Let's not forget the spacious backyard, providing spaces for entertaining or potential workshops desired! It also features a storage shed, covered & open patio, natural grass, and citrus trees to enjoy fresh fruits. Added perks are the RV gate & parking! Don't miss this opportunity!
